text: Francisco "Fran" Martínez García (born September 9, 1995 in Elche, Spain) is a Spanish footballer who currently plays for Orihuela.Fran Martínez se incorpora a la disciplina del Orihuela C.F.‚ orihuelaclubdefutbol.com, 10 January 2017 ==Career== ===Professional=== After spending time in Spain with Valencia B and Real Murcia, Martínez trialled with MLS side New York City FC.http://skyscraperblues.com/2015/02/13/potential-players-still-join-new- york-city/ However, he later signed with NYCFC's United Soccer League affiliate club Wilmington Hammerheads on April 22, 2015.http://www.wilmingtonhammerheads.com/fran-martinez-joins-hammerheads/ ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish footballers Category:Spanish expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States Category:Wilmington Hammerheads FC players Category:USL Championship players Category:Association football defenders
